    <item>
      <title>美联储博斯蒂克表示下次降息可能还要一段时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/fed-s-bostic-says-he-wants-to-wait-a-while-before-next-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚特兰大联邦储备银行行长拉斐尔博斯蒂克表示，由于 2025 年美国经济走向存在不确定性，他希望在继去年降息之后“等待一段时间”再度降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/fed-s-bostic-says-he-wants-to-wait-a-while-before-next-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 18:00:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>信贷投资者考虑抛售债券以应对关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/the-big-dilemma-in-credit-is-how-to-get-ahead-of-tariff-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着特朗普政府将关税威胁变成现实，信贷投资者面临着一个选择：出售受影响公司的债券以避免进一步损失，还是押注这些企业足够强大，能够抵御风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/the-big-dilemma-in-credit-is-how-to-get-ahead-of-tariff-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 13:15:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
